00:32:31.133 --> 00:32:32.050 align:middle line:10%
>> ROSS: That's right.

00:32:32.050 --> 00:32:34.710 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And in fact, we
were never supposed to be run

00:32:34.710 --> 00:32:36.810 align:middle line:90%
by the lower mind.

00:32:36.810 --> 00:32:40.788 align:middle line:84%
It was always to have been the
higher mind that informed us

00:32:40.788 --> 00:32:43.080 align:middle line:84%
in this third dimensional
world to not bump into things

00:32:43.080 --> 00:32:46.950 align:middle line:84%
or know when something's
on sale over at Target.

00:32:46.950 --> 00:32:50.430 align:middle line:84%
And so this data that
we're getting with AI

00:32:50.430 --> 00:32:52.360 align:middle line:90%
is all feeding the lower mind.

00:32:52.360 --> 00:32:58.590 align:middle line:10%
How are we going to preserve
the story and the notion

00:32:58.590 --> 00:33:00.720 align:middle line:10%
that each of us has to
connect with the higher

00:33:00.720 --> 00:33:05.310 align:middle line:10%
mind/soul in order to fulfill
what we're here to do, to love

00:33:05.310 --> 00:33:07.650 align:middle line:10%
life, to love each other?

00:33:07.650 --> 00:33:10.210 align:middle line:84%
>> ROSS: I hope your audience
knows how lucky they are.

00:33:10.210 --> 00:33:12.160 align:middle line:84%
You don't even
really need a guest.

00:33:12.160 --> 00:33:14.080 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: No, you and
I are just in lockstep.

00:33:14.080 --> 00:33:17.860 align:middle line:84%
>> ROSS: You are so profound in
sharing what you just shared.

00:33:17.860 --> 00:33:23.490 align:middle line:10%
This is where I have often said
and expressed my philosophy.

00:33:23.490 --> 00:33:29.550 align:middle line:84%
And that is having
that beautiful heart.

00:33:29.550 --> 00:33:31.510 align:middle line:10%
And what do I mean by that?

00:33:31.510 --> 00:33:33.100 align:middle line:10%
A heart filled with beauty.

00:33:33.100 --> 00:33:36.240 align:middle line:84%
It was said by the ancients, if
you don't have beauty within,

00:33:36.240 --> 00:33:38.790 align:middle line:84%
you don't recognize
beauty without.

00:33:38.790 --> 00:33:43.020 align:middle line:84%
That is why people who are
defacing and painting on walls,

00:33:43.020 --> 00:33:48.150 align:middle line:84%
they don't have that beauty
within to appreciate that.

00:33:48.150 --> 00:33:51.090 align:middle line:10%
And so my philosophy
has always been,

00:33:51.090 --> 00:33:54.290 align:middle line:10%
and which did come
from a dream, when

00:33:54.290 --> 00:33:58.950 align:middle line:10%
one has a beautiful heart and an
open mind and a humble spirit,

00:33:58.950 --> 00:34:06.860 align:middle line:10%
you are focused in to coming
from the heart and not the mind.

00:34:06.860 --> 00:34:10.130 align:middle line:84%
Because the second thing
I said with the open mind

00:34:10.130 --> 00:34:13.760 align:middle line:84%
is to be totally in
the moment without

00:34:13.760 --> 00:34:16.139 align:middle line:90%
any preconceived notions.

00:34:16.139 --> 00:34:20.610 align:middle line:10%
And when you're there, open
with a beautiful heart,

00:34:20.610 --> 00:34:22.820 align:middle line:10%
operating from the
standpoint that I

00:34:22.820 --> 00:34:25.550 align:middle line:10%
am going to let
love guide me, I'm

00:34:25.550 --> 00:34:28.760 align:middle line:10%
going to do everything
with love, in love,

00:34:28.760 --> 00:34:33.850 align:middle line:10%
and through love, you are
working from that heart rather

00:34:33.850 --> 00:34:34.820 align:middle line:10%
than just the mind.

00:34:34.820 --> 00:34:38.170 align:middle line:10%
The mind will say, hey, I'm not
going to make any money if I

00:34:38.170 --> 00:34:40.560 align:middle line:10%
give this away or if I do this.

00:34:40.560 --> 00:34:41.360 align:middle line:90%
Wait a minute.

00:34:41.360 --> 00:34:44.500 align:middle line:84%
I'm taking my time to
go and help this person.

00:34:44.500 --> 00:34:46.639 align:middle line:90%
That is working for the mind.

00:34:46.639 --> 00:34:49.690 align:middle line:84%
But when you're
working from love,

00:34:49.690 --> 00:34:53.380 align:middle line:84%
you're not calculating
and using the mind

00:34:53.380 --> 00:34:54.739 align:middle line:90%
that you just mentioned.

00:34:54.739 --> 00:34:57.940 align:middle line:10%
You're not using that mind
because basically our mind would

00:34:57.940 --> 00:35:02.630 align:middle line:10%
say, wait a minute, I was going
to take my time to do this,

00:35:02.630 --> 00:35:06.730 align:middle line:10%
and now my friend called
and wants me to help them?

00:35:06.730 --> 00:35:08.600 align:middle line:10%
I'm not going to do that.

00:35:08.600 --> 00:35:14.210 align:middle line:10%
That is when we're thinking
from our mind and calculating.

00:35:14.210 --> 00:35:16.690 align:middle line:84%
But when we're coming
from the heart, when

00:35:16.690 --> 00:35:20.400 align:middle line:84%
we're doing things in love,
then everything changes.

00:35:20.400 --> 00:35:22.400 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: You say, let
me finish my cup of tea,

00:35:22.400 --> 00:35:23.200 align:middle line:90%
then I'll be over.

00:35:23.200 --> 00:35:24.550 align:middle line:90%
>> ROSS: Yes, yes.

00:35:24.550 --> 00:35:28.760 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: No, but absolutely,
I understand what you're saying.

00:35:28.760 --> 00:35:31.112 align:middle line:90%
And so the problem--

00:35:31.112 --> 00:35:32.820 align:middle line:84%
and you just mentioned
something, beauty.

00:35:32.820 --> 00:35:35.220 align:middle line:84%
And beauty is a big
part of what you say.

00:35:35.220 --> 00:35:36.640 align:middle line:90%
A beautiful heart.

00:35:36.640 --> 00:35:38.760 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people
listening to this

00:35:38.760 --> 00:35:41.530 align:middle line:84%
even is like, but how do
I think through my heart?

00:35:41.530 --> 00:35:44.080 align:middle line:10%
So I led a little
meditation recently,

00:35:44.080 --> 00:35:47.070 align:middle line:10%
just a little brief one in
which I said, OK, just close

00:35:47.070 --> 00:35:49.110 align:middle line:10%
your eyes, think of some
thought that's maybe

00:35:49.110 --> 00:35:51.640 align:middle line:10%
a little challenging, irksome,
just a little weighty,

00:35:51.640 --> 00:35:52.750 align:middle line:10%
doesn't really matter.

00:35:52.750 --> 00:35:55.000 align:middle line:10%
And just close your eyes,
breathe a little bit.

00:35:55.000 --> 00:35:58.270 align:middle line:84%
And then now drop that heart,
that down into your heart.

00:35:58.270 --> 00:36:01.860 align:middle line:84%
Just take the thought and
visibly see yourself drop it,

00:36:01.860 --> 00:36:04.740 align:middle line:84%
kerplunk into the heart and
sit with it for a moment

00:36:04.740 --> 00:36:07.380 align:middle line:84%
and see what your thought
becomes, because it

00:36:07.380 --> 00:36:08.300 align:middle line:90%
changes your thoughts.

00:36:08.300 --> 00:36:09.100 align:middle line:90%
>> ROSS: Yes.

00:36:09.100 --> 00:36:10.660 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: It softens.

00:36:10.660 --> 00:36:13.150 align:middle line:84%
Judgment usually is the
first thing that goes away.

00:36:13.150 --> 00:36:14.830 align:middle line:90%
And that's what they said.

00:36:14.830 --> 00:36:17.470 align:middle line:84%
That is how-- that
is our destiny.

00:36:17.470 --> 00:36:21.400 align:middle line:10%
That is how humanity is going
to be living in the future.

00:36:21.400 --> 00:36:25.660 align:middle line:10%
>> ROSS: Well, and again, I
subscribe to what you're saying.

00:36:25.660 --> 00:36:31.920 align:middle line:10%
And when you do the things with
love, in love, and through love,

00:36:31.920 --> 00:36:34.770 align:middle line:10%
that's the equivalent of
dropping into the heart.

00:36:34.770 --> 00:36:39.600 align:middle line:10%
So there's two ways you
can take whatever that,

00:36:39.600 --> 00:36:42.960 align:middle line:10%
you know, I don't even
look at them as obstacles.

00:36:42.960 --> 00:36:47.750 align:middle line:84%
I look at things, challenges
as opportunities to grow.

00:36:47.750 --> 00:36:49.250 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: A good
way to look at it.

00:36:49.250 --> 00:36:54.200 align:middle line:84%
>> ROSS: And somebody can fall
on their face because something

00:36:54.200 --> 00:36:56.400 align:middle line:84%
brought them down
to their knees,

00:36:56.400 --> 00:36:58.860 align:middle line:84%
or there was a
big boulder there.

00:36:58.860 --> 00:37:03.710 align:middle line:10%
And I guess the higher precept
would be to look at it and go,

00:37:03.710 --> 00:37:08.040 align:middle line:10%
my soul has brought me
to learn a lesson here.

00:37:08.040 --> 00:37:10.400 align:middle line:84%
Gosh, from this
angle, the world looks

00:37:10.400 --> 00:37:12.600 align:middle line:84%
a little different with
my face on the floor.

00:37:12.600 --> 00:37:13.800 align:middle line:90%
I never thought of looking--

00:37:13.800 --> 00:37:15.140 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah, that's right.

00:37:15.140 --> 00:37:18.600 align:middle line:84%
>> ROSS: What direction
are we going to go?

00:37:18.600 --> 00:37:24.050 align:middle line:84%
There are creative opportunities
to express and grow, even

00:37:24.050 --> 00:37:26.220 align:middle line:84%
though on the surface
there may be a challenge.

00:37:26.220 --> 00:37:31.700 align:middle line:84%
Now, all of this does fit
in because, again, I asked,

00:37:31.700 --> 00:37:33.170 align:middle line:90%
why are we here?

00:37:33.170 --> 00:37:35.330 align:middle line:10%
Why do people
believe we're here?

00:37:35.330 --> 00:37:41.000 align:middle line:84%
Is it to stuff all kinds
of knowledge and data

00:37:41.000 --> 00:37:43.990 align:middle line:84%
into our faces and then
we go, and somebody goes,

00:37:43.990 --> 00:37:48.020 align:middle line:84%
you know what, you
cross over into spirit,

00:37:48.020 --> 00:37:50.030 align:middle line:84%
you didn't even
store it in yourself.

00:37:50.030 --> 00:37:52.520 align:middle line:90%
You had it in a hand device.

00:37:52.520 --> 00:37:55.330 align:middle line:84%
So that does not
make a lot of sense

00:37:55.330 --> 00:37:58.810 align:middle line:84%
even for people on the
spiritual path to really-- you

00:37:58.810 --> 00:38:00.860 align:middle line:90%
need to think about that.

00:38:00.860 --> 00:38:03.380 align:middle line:90%
Where has the gain really come?

00:38:03.380 --> 00:38:05.470 align:middle line:90%
The computer told you to do it.

00:38:05.470 --> 00:38:08.545 align:middle line:84%
It's like the devil
made me do it.

00:38:08.545 --> 00:38:10.400 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: What are
we here for then?

00:38:10.400 --> 00:38:13.060 align:middle line:84%
Why is every human
being on this planet

00:38:13.060 --> 00:38:16.240 align:middle line:84%
right now, right now in
these unique times even?

00:38:16.240 --> 00:38:19.700 align:middle line:84%
>> ROSS: My opinion, and
it's, again, only my opinion,

00:38:19.700 --> 00:38:24.190 align:middle line:84%
my frame of reference, we are
here to demonstrate how we use

00:38:24.190 --> 00:38:27.370 align:middle line:84%
the creative
energies that we are.

00:38:27.370 --> 00:38:31.170 align:middle line:84%
Now, that does not mean you
have to be a singer or a dancer

00:38:31.170 --> 00:38:32.320 align:middle line:90%
or write books.

00:38:32.320 --> 00:38:35.670 align:middle line:10%
What do you do in
your daily life?

00:38:35.670 --> 00:38:41.550 align:middle line:10%
Are you creating within
yourself a greater understanding

00:38:41.550 --> 00:38:44.970 align:middle line:10%
of your place in the
cosmos, your place

00:38:44.970 --> 00:38:48.360 align:middle line:10%
with interacting with
the other souls that are

00:38:48.360 --> 00:38:50.800 align:middle line:10%
with you on this planet Earth?

00:38:50.800 --> 00:38:54.330 align:middle line:84%
Are you planting-- not creating,
but planting flowers or creating

00:38:54.330 --> 00:38:57.030 align:middle line:90%
ground swells with the energy?

00:38:57.030 --> 00:38:59.740 align:middle line:90%
To me, this is why we're here.

00:38:59.740 --> 00:39:02.290 align:middle line:84%
How do we manage
that creative energy?

00:39:02.290 --> 00:39:07.660 align:middle line:10%
Now, a greater discussion is
what we're actually capable of.

00:39:07.660 --> 00:39:11.550 align:middle line:10%
And that is people
have locked themselves

00:39:11.550 --> 00:39:14.190 align:middle line:10%
in because you're
not supposed to-- now

00:39:14.190 --> 00:39:15.910 align:middle line:10%
we're going the opposite way.

00:39:15.910 --> 00:39:18.400 align:middle line:84%
You can't think for
yourself anymore.

00:39:18.400 --> 00:39:23.530 align:middle line:84%
And if you do this and you're
out of the box, that's not good.

00:39:23.530 --> 00:39:28.220 align:middle line:10%
And so a discussion I had
recently, if people's belief

00:39:28.220 --> 00:39:31.160 align:middle line:10%
system is, it's going to
take X amount of years

00:39:31.160 --> 00:39:35.155 align:middle line:10%
to learn something, that's how
long it takes for an individual.

00:39:35.155 --> 00:39:36.530 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: The
belief will trump.

00:39:36.530 --> 00:39:40.370 align:middle line:10%
>> ROSS: The belief, so I,
in all of our shows together,

00:39:40.370 --> 00:39:42.530 align:middle line:10%
have tried to empower
people to understand,

00:39:42.530 --> 00:39:49.760 align:middle line:10%
you have no conception of what
you're capable of unless you

00:39:49.760 --> 00:39:55.460 align:middle line:10%
bring it into your awareness and
understand that we are unlimited

00:39:55.460 --> 00:40:02.180 align:middle line:10%
in our potential if we go within
and recognize we are greater

00:40:02.180 --> 00:40:08.580 align:middle line:10%
than this physical body, we are
greater than any AI or computer.

00:40:08.580 --> 00:40:11.570 align:middle line:10%
We have unlimited potential.

00:40:11.570 --> 00:40:16.590 align:middle line:84%
If we bring our view
into that arena,

00:40:16.590 --> 00:40:19.680 align:middle line:84%
rather than trying to figure
out, how can I do this faster?

00:40:19.680 --> 00:40:20.480 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:40:20.480 --> 00:40:23.580 align:middle line:84%
You're absolutely-- beautifully
said, absolutely true.

00:40:23.580 --> 00:40:26.290 align:middle line:10%
And there's some encouraging
stuff happening in pop culture

00:40:26.290 --> 00:40:27.090 align:middle line:10%
right now.

00:40:27.090 --> 00:40:30.550 align:middle line:84%
I came across something and I
thought, oh, I can't watch this.

00:40:30.550 --> 00:40:31.780 align:middle line:90%
And I thought, watch it.

00:40:31.780 --> 00:40:33.130 align:middle line:90%
And I'm glad I did.

00:40:33.130 --> 00:40:36.970 align:middle line:10%
It's really for teens and people
in their young 20s, pretty much.

00:40:36.970 --> 00:40:38.800 align:middle line:90%
It features the Gen-Z.

00:40:38.800 --> 00:40:39.600 align:middle line:90%
>> ROSS: Yes.

00:40:39.600 --> 00:40:40.400 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: OK.

00:40:40.400 --> 00:40:43.530 align:middle line:84%
And it's a show on
Netflix called Uglies.

00:40:43.530 --> 00:40:47.430 align:middle line:84%
And what it is, is they
decided the world is now

00:40:47.430 --> 00:40:49.980 align:middle line:84%
harmonious and peaceful
because we've eliminated

00:40:49.980 --> 00:40:51.610 align:middle line:90%
all of our differences.

00:40:51.610 --> 00:40:55.450 align:middle line:84%
And the final one is to
eliminate aesthetic differences.

00:40:55.450 --> 00:40:59.190 align:middle line:84%
Everyone on their 16th birthday
has an operation where they

00:40:59.190 --> 00:41:02.740 align:middle line:84%
become their idealized,
beautiful self, sparkling.

00:41:02.740 --> 00:41:05.910 align:middle line:10%
Choose the color of eyes,
they're all choosing gold.

00:41:05.910 --> 00:41:09.400 align:middle line:10%
And eyes, everything
to be perfect.

00:41:09.400 --> 00:41:13.440 align:middle line:84%
And so the uglies are those
who haven't reached their 16th

00:41:13.440 --> 00:41:16.810 align:middle line:84%
birthday, and there's a
counter-rebellion saying,

00:41:16.810 --> 00:41:20.550 align:middle line:84%
I don't want the operation
because what it does is it takes

00:41:20.550 --> 00:41:22.300 align:middle line:90%
everything and flattens it.

00:41:22.300 --> 00:41:23.680 align:middle line:90%
Everyone's alike.

00:41:23.680 --> 00:41:26.120 align:middle line:84%
People don't think for
themselves anymore.

00:41:26.120 --> 00:41:28.620 align:middle line:84%
Any kind of contrast
is eliminated.

00:41:28.620 --> 00:41:32.460 align:middle line:10%
And the heroes are the
uglies who have chosen this--

00:41:32.460 --> 00:41:34.970 align:middle line:10%
I won't give the plot away--
to go the other direction

00:41:34.970 --> 00:41:36.420 align:middle line:10%
and refuse the operation.

00:41:36.420 --> 00:41:40.160 align:middle line:84%
This is a really kind of,
in-your-face, wonderful

00:41:40.160 --> 00:41:41.810 align:middle line:90%
Gen-Z message, I think.

00:41:41.810 --> 00:41:43.330 align:middle line:90%
They want to stay authentic.

00:41:43.330 --> 00:41:44.130 align:middle line:90%
>> ROSS: Yes.

