but do you remember
the old Twilight Zone?

00:41:48.630 --> 00:41:49.140 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Oh, yeah, yeah.

00:41:49.140 --> 00:41:49.980 align:middle line:90%
>> ROSS: With Rod Sterling?

00:41:49.980 --> 00:41:51.313 align:middle line:10%
>> REGINA: --Rod Sterling, yeah.

00:41:51.313 --> 00:41:55.020 align:middle line:10%
>> ROSS: So there was a great
episode where it starts off,

00:41:55.020 --> 00:41:57.870 align:middle line:10%
