00:42:58.930 --> 00:43:01.780 align:middle line:10%
that this ability
of the human being

00:43:01.780 --> 00:43:04.780 align:middle line:10%
to take our mind, our
creativity, and everything,

00:43:04.780 --> 00:43:08.230 align:middle line:10%
and run it through
that pristine lens life

00:43:08.230 --> 00:43:12.280 align:middle line:10%
force, the heart itself will be
the thing that will distinguish

00:43:12.280 --> 00:43:16.850 align:middle line:10%
us from AI no matter how real
it starts appearing to be.

00:43:16.850 --> 00:43:19.160 align:middle line:10%
>> ROSS: Yes, I do
want to share a dream.

00:43:19.160 --> 00:43:20.420 align:middle line:90%
I think we're at the end.

00:43:20.420 --> 00:43:25.060 align:middle line:84%
And a dream which I had,
this was 14 years ago.

00:43:25.060 --> 00:43:29.400 align:middle line:84%
I was walking, again, maybe I
put it on a show, previous show.

00:43:29.400 --> 00:43:32.410 align:middle line:84%
I was walking with all the
truth-seekers of the world.

00:43:32.410 --> 00:43:33.730 align:middle line:90%
We were walking together.

00:43:33.730 --> 00:43:35.050 align:middle line:90%
They weren't following me.

00:43:35.050 --> 00:43:36.780 align:middle line:10%
And in the distance,
we saw a woman

00:43:36.780 --> 00:43:39.850 align:middle line:10%
dressed in blue
holding a microphone,

00:43:39.850 --> 00:43:44.350 align:middle line:10%
and she was partially
covered with a fog or smoke.

00:43:44.350 --> 00:43:49.110 align:middle line:10%
And as we got up to her, it was
Sophia, the goddess of wisdom.

00:43:49.110 --> 00:43:52.470 align:middle line:84%
And to my right or her
left were horseshoe

00:43:52.470 --> 00:43:55.380 align:middle line:84%
stands with all the book
authors and the people

00:43:55.380 --> 00:43:57.700 align:middle line:90%
with courses and the lecturers.

00:43:57.700 --> 00:44:01.030 align:middle line:84%
And I am not saying what
they were saying was false,

00:44:01.030 --> 00:44:04.300 align:middle line:84%
but they all had only
a piece of the story.

00:44:04.300 --> 00:44:08.340 align:middle line:84%
And their words, their
smoke was covering her.

00:44:08.340 --> 00:44:11.520 align:middle line:84%
And I wondered at
that moment, what

00:44:11.520 --> 00:44:16.030 align:middle line:84%
are we supposed to do
to find absolute truth?

00:44:16.030 --> 00:44:19.020 align:middle line:10%
And a big wind
blew off the ocean.

00:44:19.020 --> 00:44:21.220 align:middle line:90%
And the following words came.

00:44:21.220 --> 00:44:25.640 align:middle line:84%
All one needs is a beautiful
heart and open mind

00:44:25.640 --> 00:44:27.690 align:middle line:90%
and a humble spirit.

00:44:27.690 --> 00:44:29.650 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Which to
me-- that's your motto.

00:44:29.650 --> 00:44:30.450 align:middle line:90%
That's you.

00:44:30.450 --> 00:44:31.880 align:middle line:90%
You live that way.

00:44:31.880 --> 00:44:32.850 align:middle line:90%
You represent that.

00:44:32.850 --> 00:44:33.650 align:middle line:90%
>> ROSS: We do.

00:44:33.650 --> 00:44:35.550 align:middle line:90%
And how do we do it?

00:44:35.550 --> 00:44:39.780 align:middle line:84%
With love, in love,
and through love.

00:44:39.780 --> 00:44:43.580 align:middle line:84%
Yes, the books are
exciting and the lecturers

00:44:43.580 --> 00:44:47.910 align:middle line:84%
are great, and the I. But
what does it boil down to?

00:44:47.910 --> 00:44:50.810 align:middle line:84%
It boils down to the
most simplistic things

00:44:50.810 --> 00:44:52.410 align:middle line:90%
that we've been discussing.

00:44:52.410 --> 00:44:55.400 align:middle line:10%
A beautiful heart is
just seeing the beauty

00:44:55.400 --> 00:44:57.140 align:middle line:10%
in every single thing.

00:44:57.140 --> 00:45:02.480 align:middle line:10%
Being open, which means in the
moment, live in the moment.

00:45:02.480 --> 00:45:05.360 align:middle line:10%
And of course, a
difficult one for a lot

00:45:05.360 --> 00:45:09.810 align:middle line:10%
of the people, high profile,
is that humble part.

00:45:09.810 --> 00:45:14.270 align:middle line:10%
Because when we're closed,
we have no fresh input

00:45:14.270 --> 00:45:15.900 align:middle line:10%
to what's coming in.

00:45:15.900 --> 00:45:21.050 align:middle line:10%
So yes, I ascribe to what
you shared with the heart

00:45:21.050 --> 00:45:22.410 align:middle line:10%
being important.

00:45:22.410 --> 00:45:24.520 align:middle line:10%
I've been directed
by my guidance

00:45:24.520 --> 00:45:31.370 align:middle line:10%
