books to reach enlightenment.

00:45:38.150 --> 00:45:39.270 align:middle line:10%
That's nonsense.

00:45:39.270 --> 00:45:40.070 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: It is.

00:45:40.070 --> 00:45:43.330 align:middle line:84%
>> ROSS: I mean, it may be fun,
