quote, a human heart,

00:45:54.520 --> 00:45:58.430 align:middle line:10%
is the secret to
greater enlightenment,

00:45:58.430 --> 00:46:01.760 align:middle line:10%
and the gifts will
come as needed.

00:46:01.760 --> 00:46:03.410 align:middle line:10%
And what do I mean by that?

00:46:03.410 --> 00:46:06.550 align:middle line:10%
When you look to help
another human being

00:46:06.550 --> 00:46:08.780 align:middle line:10%
and you're coming
from the heart,

00:46:08.780 --> 00:46:11.060 align:middle line:10%
you can do miraculous things.

00:46:11.060 --> 00:46:12.380 align:middle line:90%
You can help heal them.

00:46:12.380 --> 00:46:12.520 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Oh, yes.

00:46:12.520 --> 00:46:13.790 align:middle line:90%
And we know that you do that.

00:46:13.790 --> 00:46:15.950 align:middle line:84%
You've done seemingly
miraculous things.

00:46:15.950 --> 00:46:17.855 align:middle line:84%
>> ROSS: And we know
that you do that.

00:46:17.855 --> 00:46:19.480 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: It's that
with you one time.

00:46:19.480 --> 00:46:21.020 align:middle line:90%
>> ROSS: That's exactly right.

00:46:21.020 --> 00:46:23.080 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: No, but that's the
gift we all have for each other.

00:46:23.080 --> 00:46:24.310 align:middle line:90%
And you're absolutely right.

00:46:24.310 --> 00:46:26.530 align:middle line:84%
Beautifully said,
everything you just said.

00:46:26.530 --> 00:46:29.050 align:middle line:84%
The fact is AI is
throughout the universe.

00:46:29.050 --> 00:46:30.430 align:middle line:90%
AI is on other planets.

00:46:30.430 --> 00:46:33.700 align:middle line:10%
